I, 1, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.108" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 108</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.134" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 134</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.150" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.1.89" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.74" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 143</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.4.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 4, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.4.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 4, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 3.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 3.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 117</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 5, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.107" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.118" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 118</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.118" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 118</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.34" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 130</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 130</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.184" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 6, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.36" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.260" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 260</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.5.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 5, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 127</bibl>. Followed by an inf.; with <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>I have --ed a thousand blushing apparitions to start into her face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.160" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 160</bibl></cit>. without <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>who --s the waxing tide grow wave by wave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 95</bibl></cit>.
